<li id="cite_note-How_May_Day_Became_a_Workers_Holiday-resolution-20"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-How_May_Day_Became_a_Workers_Holiday-resolution_20-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/dna/h2g2/A627662">"How May Day Became a Workers' Holiday"</a>. <i>The Guide to Life, The Universe and Everything</i>. BBC. October 4, 2001<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">January 19,</span> 2008</span>. <q>(It is) Resolved ... that eight hours shall constitute a legal day's labor from and after May 1, 1886, and that we recommend to labor organizations throughout this district that they so direct their laws so as to conform to this resolution by the time named.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Guide+to+Life%2C+The+Universe+and+Everything&amp;rft.atitle=How+May+Day+Became+a+Workers%27+Holiday&amp;rft.date=2001-10-04&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fdna%2Fh2g2%2FA627662&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHaymarket+affair" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-How_May_Day_Became_a_Workers_Holiday-strike-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-How_May_Day_Became_a_Workers_Holiday-strike_21-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/dna/h2g2/A627662">"How May Day Became a Workers' Holiday"</a>. <i>The Guide to Life, The Universe and Everything</i>. BBC. October 4, 2001<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">January 19,</span> 2008</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Guide+to+Life%2C+The+Universe+and+Everything&amp;rft.atitle=How+May+Day+Became+a+Workers%27+Holiday&amp;rft.date=2001-10-04&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fdna%2Fh2g2%2FA627662&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHaymarket+affair" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
